    "content": "-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n                    Built This City  - Jefferson Starship\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nI'm pretty sure that the bass for this song is actually a half step down so it\r\nmight not sound 100% with the recording but it sounds very accurate.\r\n\r\n[tab]       Intro\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------------------------2----3----------|  X 2\r\nA|-------------1--------0---------------------------1------------------------|\r\nE|-------1--------------------3--------------1-------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n[tab]       Verse\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|---1--11---1--11---1--11----1--11-----1---11---1---11-----1--11--1--11-----|\r\n      I'm pretty sure you just play F the entire time on bass. It \r\n      should be in time with the bass drum. Sounds good but kinda boring to play.[/tab]\r\n\r\n       \r\n[tab]G|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|---1--11--1--11----1---11---1--11----------1-----0-----0-------------------|\r\n                                                        ^^^\r\n                                   This last note should really be Eb, but in\r\n   standard tuning, I just hold out the E a little longer. If you wanted to,\r\n   I guess you could play Eb 6th fret of A string but it's a really quick note that's\r\n   difficult to notice anyway.[/tab]\r\n    \r\n[tab]   Prechorus   (Marconi plays the mamba!)\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|----5-5--5-55------------------------33-3-------------------1111-----------|\r\nE|----------------66-6-----1-1--1-11------------------1111-------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------------------------------------3---|\r\nA|-------------1-------0---------------------------1-------------------------|\r\nE|-----1----------------------3-----------1--------------------1----0--------|[/tab]\r\n[tab]   Chorus\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|  X 2\r\nA|--1-1-11-1--11----0-0-00-0-------------------0--1------------------ -------| \r\nE|--------------------------------1------3------------------------------ ----|[/tab]\r\n         \r\n[tab]   Bridge (It's just another Sunday...)\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------3------------3-----2--3-----------------------------------------|  X 4\r\nA|-----0-0-------0--0-1------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\n   For that little solo bit play Bb and play F when exiting the bridge.[/tab]\r\n\r\n   Those are all the parts. Just figure out the timings.\r\n\r\n\r\n===============================================================================",
